 also foreshadows what awaits the soul as it embarks on its 'soul mission' on Planet Earth. In this book, the two realms--which are so often mistakenly portrayed as polar opposites--seamlessly co-exist alongside each other. This book awakens us to the world of the spirit. To our spirit. To our calling. <br /><br />I wanted this book to be read to be out loud by the author before I went to sleep. There is a spirit in the book that embodies the soul of the ancient storytellers, and yet it is still perfectly applicable for modern times. <i>The Little Light</i> is a truly timeless tale. <br /><br />This short book is about so many things that it seems pointless for me to explain what it is all about. Get yourself a copy, open its pages and allow yourself to embark on a journey that will forever leave you unchanged. </span></div></div></div></section></section><section class="ReviewCard__tags"></section><footer class="SocialFooter"><div data-testid="stats" class="SocialFooter__statsContainer"><div class="Button__container"><button type="button" class="Button Button--inline Button--small Button--subdued"><span class="Button__labelItem">12 likes</span></button></div></div><div data-testid="actions"><div class="SocialFooter__action"><div class="Button__container"><button type="button" class="Button Button--inline Button--small"><span class="Button__labelItem"><i class="Icon LikeIcon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M14.4813282,6.41129383 L14.586127,6.97676447 C14.5964421,7.03541935 14.6071117,7.09675198 14.6181364,7.1607667 L14.8551301,8.60363442 L17.440983,8.60363442 C18.1623576,8.60363442 18.8218187,9.01120377 19.1444272,9.65642083 L19.1708204,9.70920723 C19.4523479,10.2722622 19.4523479,10.9350066 19.1708204,11.4980616 L19.118034,11.6036344 L19.1708204,11.7092072 C19.4523479,12.2722622 19.4523479,12.9350066 19.1708204,13.4980616 L19.118034,13.6036344 L19.1708204,13.7092072 C19.4523479,14.2722622 19.4523479,14.9350066 19.1708204,15.4980616 L19,15.8397024 L19,16.1036344 